column4: <content>Death of the Virgin. The Louvre drawing (Lugt, Inventaire ...Maîtres des Anciens Pays-Bas nés avant 1550, [Paris: Éditions des musées nationaux], 1968, N° 274) is a copy after the Upton House picture, not after the print (see especially the back of the chair in the foreground). Lugt puts forward other arguments for copy after painting and reject the theory of M. Jaffé (who reproduces the Louvre drawing in his article in Master Drawings 'Rubens as a collector of Drawings') that the drawing was retouched by Rubens.</content>
<documentation.title>Musée du Louvre : inventaire général des dessins des écoles du Nord : maîtres des anciens Pays-Bas nés avant 1550</documentation.title>
